  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      European prospective one day cohort study. Analysis of the prevalence of frailty and
      predefined 30-day postoperative complications in adult patients undergoing emergency or
      elective surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
